POST http://localhost:3000/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Ana Lopez",
    "email": "ana.test@iteso.mx",
    "password": "password123",
    "confirm_password": "password123"
}

### Registro de Instructor (Código Correcto)
POST http://localhost:3000/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Instructor Pro",
    "email": "coach@fitnow.com",
    "password": "password123",
    "confirm_password": "password123",
    "rol": "instructor",
    "codigo": "FITNOW2026"
}

